Daruruwan da aka kashe da girgizar kasashen Indonesia, tsunami, tare da yawan adadin da aka gani ya tashi
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu, mutane da yawa sun tashi yayin da manyan raƙuman ruwa suka fadi a rairayin bakin teku, lokacin da babbar girgizar kasa da tsunami ta shafa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia, hukumomi suka ce a ranar Asabar.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru don biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu a ranar Juma'a lokacin da raƙuman ruwa suka kai mita shida (18 feet) a kan teku a cikin daskarewa, suna kwance mutane da yawa har zuwa mutuwarsu da kuma hallaka wani abu a hanyarsu.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar kasa mai girma 7.5.
"Lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta taso a jiya, mutane har yanzu suna yin ayyukansu a bakin rairayin bakin teku kuma ba su gudu nan da nan kuma sun zama abin shafa ba," in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, kakakin hukumar rage bala'i ta Indonesia BNPB.
"Tsunami bai zo da kansa ba, ya jan motoci, lokuta, gidaje, ya buga duk abin da ke ƙasa," in ji Nugroho, ya kara da cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya a bakin teku da sauri na 800 kph (497 mph) kafin ya buge bakin teku.
Wasu mutane sun hau bishiyoyi don tserewa daga tsunami kuma suka tsira, in ji shi.
An kwashe mutane 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyin 24 a Palu.
Hotunan jirgin sama da hukumar bala'i ta fitar sun nuna gine-gine da shagunan da yawa da aka hallaka, gadoji sun rushe kuma sun rushe da masallaci da ke kewaye da ruwa.
A ranar Asabar ne ya ci gaba da kaddamar da birnin da ke bakin teku.
An ji jerin girgizar ƙasa a wani yanki da mutane miliyan 2.4.
Hukumar Kimantawa da Aikace-aikacen Fasaha ta Indonesia (BPPT) ta ce a cikin sanarwar makamashi da aka fitar da babbar girgizar ta ranar Juma'a ya kusan sau 200 da wutar lantarki ta bam a kan Hiroshima a yakin duniya na biyu.
Gidajen birnin, wanda ke zaune a ƙarshen wani wuri mai tsawo, mai zurfi, zai iya girman girman tsunami, in ji shi.
Nugroho ya bayyana lalacewa a matsayin "mafi yawa" kuma ya ce dubban gidaje, asibitoci, ma'aikatan kasuwanci da hotels sun rushe.
An samo gawawwakin wasu wadanda suka mutu a karkashin rushewar gine-gine, in ji shi, inda ya kara da cewa mutane 540 suka ji rauni kuma 29 suka rasa.
Nugroho ya ce wadanda suka mutu da lalacewa za su iya zama mafi girma a bakin teku na kilomita 300 (190 miles) arewacin Palu, wani yanki mai suna Donggala, wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar.
Sadarwa "Babu cikakke ba tare da bayanai" daga Donggala, in ji Nugroho.
Akwai mutane sama da 300,000 da ke zaune a can," in ji Red Cross a wata sanarwa, inda ya kara da cewa ma'aikatanta da masu sa kai suna tafiya zuwa yankunan da suka shafa.
"Wannan bala'i ne, amma zai iya zama mafi muni," in ji shi.
