Amurka ta bukaci biyan kuɗin AI.
Kamar yadda kasar Sin ta zama mai aiki a cikin fasahar wucin gadi, Amurka ya kamata ta ninka adadin da ta kashe akan bincike a filin, in ji mai saka hannun jari da kuma mai aikin AI Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki ga Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Jawabin sun zo ne bayan sassan daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka sun yi sanarwar AI, kodayake Amurka ba ta da dabarun AI na yau da kullun.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta a shekarar da ta gabata: tana nufin zama No.1 a cikin ƙirƙirar AI ta 2030.
"Duba kasafin kudin binciken AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda duk sauran ƙasashe suna da nisa a bayan Amurka, kuma muna neman ci gaba na gaba a AI," in ji Lee.
Sauya kudade na iya sau biyu da yiwuwar cewa babban nasarar AI na gaba za a yi a Amurka, Lee ya gaya wa CNBC a wata hira a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley da Sabuwar Tsarin Duniya" ya buga wannan watan ta Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a China, Face+.
A cikin 1980s a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke dan wasan Othello na Amurka mafi girma, sannan daga baya ya kasance zartarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban reshe na Google China.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata kamar Kalubalen Robotics na Agency of Defense Advanced Research Projects kuma ya tambayi lokacin da na gaba zai kasance, don taimakawa wajen gano masu hangen nesa na gaba.
Masu bincike a Amurka sau da yawa suna buƙatar yin aiki tuƙuru don samun tallafin gwamnati, in ji Lee.
"Ba shine kasar Sin da ke cire shugabannin ilimi ba; kamfanoni ne," in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun hayar fitilu daga jami'o'i don aiki akan AI a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce canje-canje na manufofin ƙaura na iya taimakawa Amurka ta ƙarfafa kokarin AI.
"Ina tsammanin dole ne a bayar da katunan kore ta atomatik ga PhD a AI," in ji shi.
Majalisar Jihar Sin ta gabatar da shirin samar da Intelligence Artificial Generation a watan Yuli na 2017.
Gidauniyar Kimiyyar Halitta ta kasar Sin tana ba da kudade ga mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi kamar yadda Gidauniyar Kimiyya ta Kasa da sauran kungiyoyin gwamnati ke ba da kudade ga masu binciken Amurka, amma ingancin aikin ilimi ya ragu a kasar Sin, in ji Lee.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Intelligence Artificial Cibiyar, wanda ake nufin ya hada da abokan hulɗa daga masana'antu da ilimi, kuma Fadar White House ta sanar da kafa Kwamitin Zaɓin Intelligence Artificial.
A wannan watan DARPA ta sanar da saka hannun jari na dala biliyan 2 a wani shirin da ake kira AI Next.
Game da NSF, a halin yanzu yana saka hannun jari fiye da dala miliyan 100 a kowace shekara a binciken AI.
A halin yanzu, dokar Amurka da ta nemi ƙirƙirar Hukumar Tsaro ta Kasa kan Intelligence Artificial ba ta ganin mataki a cikin watanni.
