"Na zo yau don kada kuri'a ga makomar kasar, ga matasa a Macedonia don su iya zama 'yanci a ƙarƙashin karkashin Tarayyar Turai saboda yana nufin rayuwa mafi aminci ga dukanmu," in ji Olivera Georgijevska, mai shekara 79, a Skopje.
