Trump na West Virginia Rally Time, YouTube Channel
Shugaban kasar Donald Trump ya fara taron yakin neman zabe yau da dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko na taron Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wuraren sada zumunci ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Tare da kuri'un da aka tabbatar da shi don zaɓar cika kotun koli, Trump yana da niyyar gina goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar lokaci na gaba tun da 'yan Republicans ke cikin haɗarin rasa iko da majalisar lokacin da aka jefa kuri'un a ranar Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne yaushe yakin neman zabe na Trump yau da kullum kuma ta yaya za a yi wasa a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump Wheeling, West Virginia don karfe 7 na yamma ET da yamma, Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ka iya kallon Trump ta West Virginia taron online kasa via live stream a YouTube.
Trump zai iya magance sauraron kotun koli na wannan makon, Bret Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama mummunan zarge-zarge da laifin rashin adalci na jima'i tare da zaɓin tabbatar da majalisar dattijai na tsawon mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincika.
Amma manufar farko na wannan taron shine taimakawa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar taba zaben Nuwamba suna samun ƙarin haɓaka.
Don haka, yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce wadannan taron guda biyar a mako mai zuwa suna nufin "inganta masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin kare da kuma fadada yawancin da suke riƙe a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai," in ji Reuters.
"Control of Congress yana da matukar muhimmanci ga shirinsa cewa shugaban kasa zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu mu shiga cikin lokacin yakin neman zabe," in ji mai magana da yawun yakin neman zabe na Trump wanda ya ƙi a sanya masa suna.
An shirya Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron yau da dare zai iya kawo magoya bayan "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma zana hoto daga kafofin watsa labarun Pittsburgh," in ji West Virginia Metro News.
Asabar ita ce karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata da Trump ya ziyarci West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe kashi 40 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan majalisar dattijai ta West Virginia Republican Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke tafiya a zaben.
"Ba wata alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban kasa dole ne ya yi kokarin ba shi ci gaba a zaben," in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
