Turai ta dauki 10-6 jagora zuwa Ryder Cup na karshe rana
Turai za ta yi amfani da lafiya a ranar karshe na gasar cin kofin Ryder bayan da ta fito daga wasannin hudu na Asabar da hudu tare da jagorancin 10-6 a kan Amurka.
Da aka ba da wahayi ga duo Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci cajin tare da nasara biyu a kan wani mai gwagwarmayar Tiger Woods don ɗaukar ƙidayarsu a Le Golf National zuwa maki huɗu.
