A shekara ta 1997, an kawar da jima'i a kasar Sin, amma ana ce wariyar launin fata a kan mutanen LGBT.
Saboda dabi'u masu rikitarwa na kasar, binciken ya kiyasta cewa kashi 70-90% na maza da ke yin jima'i tare da maza za su auri mata.
