Brexit: Birtaniya za ta yi nadama har abada don rasa masu mota
Birtaniya "Za ta yi nadama har abada" idan ta rasa matsayinta a matsayin shugaban duniya a cikin masana'antar mota bayan Brexit, Sakataren Kasuwanci Greg Clark ya ce.
Ya kara da cewa Toyota UK ta gaya wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba za ta dakatar da samarwa na dan lokaci a masana'antarta a Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
"Muna buƙatar yarjejeniyar," in ji Mr. Clark.
Ma'aikatar motar Japan ta ce tasirin jinkirin iyaka idan babu yarjejeniyar Brexit zai iya kashe ayyukan.
Kamfanin Burnaston - wanda ya sa Toyota ta Auris da Avensis - ya samar da kusan motoci 150,000 a shekarar da ta gabata wanda aka fitar da kashi 90 cikin 100 zuwa sauran Tarayyar Turai.
"Ina ra'ayin cewa idan Birtaniya ta hallaka daga Tarayyar Turai a karshen watan Maris zamu ga dakatar da samarwa a masana'antarmu," in ji Marvin Cooke, darektan kula da Toyota a Burnaston.
Sauran masana'antun motocin Birtaniya sun taso da tsoro game da barin EU ba tare da yarjejeniyar yadda kasuwancin ketare ba zai yi aiki, ciki har da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover.
Alal misali, BMW ta ce za ta rufe shuka na Mini a Oxford na wata daya bayan Brexit.
Babban damuwa game da abin da masu mota suka ce shine haɗarin samar da sarkar sadarwa idan babu wani yarjejeniyar Brexit.
Ana gudanar da layin samar da Toyota a kan tushen "mai-lokaci," tare da sassa suna isa kowane minti 37 daga masu samar da kayayyaki a Birtaniya da EU don motoci da aka ba da umarni.
Idan Birtaniya ta bar Tarayyar Turai ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba a ranar 29 ga watan Maris, zai iya faruwa a kan iyakar da masana'antar ta ce zai iya haifar da jinkirin da raguwa na sassa.
Ba zai yiwu ba ga Toyota dauki fiye da rana darajar kayan a cikin Derbyshire shuka, kamfanin ya ce, kuma haka za a dakatar da samar.
Mista Clark ya ce shirin Chequers na Theresa May don dangantaka da Tarayyar Turai a nan gaba yana "daidaitawa don kauce wa waɗannan ra'ayoyin a kan iyaka."
"Muna buƙatar yin yarjejeniyar. Muna so mu sami mafi kyawun yarjejeniyar da za ta ba da izinin kamar yadda na ce ba kawai nasarar da ake samu a yanzu ba, amma don mu gano wannan damar," in ji shirin BBC Radio 4 na Yau.
"Abokan shaida daga ba kawai Toyota amma wasu masana'antun sune cewa muna buƙatar mu sami damar ci gaba da abin da ya kasance babban nasarar sarƙoƙin samar."
Toyota ba ta iya faɗi tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da samar da samfurin ba, amma a cikin dogon lokaci, ta yi gargadi cewa ƙarin farashin zai rage gasar shuka da kuma karshe kudin ayyuka.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston tsawon shekaru 24 kuma shi ne mai kiran haɗin gwiwa a cikin shuka, ya ce mambobinsa sun ƙara damuwa: "A cikin kwarewa na da zarar waɗannan ayyukan ba su dawo ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun gwamnati ya ce: "Mun gabatar da shirin da ya dace da cikakken dangantakarmu na nan gaba tare da EU."
