Ruwa da tsunami a Indonesia
An kashe mutane akalla 384 da wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da ta kai garin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, tare da adadin mutuwar da ake tsammani ya tashi.
Tare da sadarwa da aka fitar, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga birnin Donggula ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane sama da 16,000 bayan bala'in ya faru.
Ga wasu mahimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggula, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Sulawesi na Tsakiya, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani ƙaramin bazara a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
Birnin ya yi bikin cika shekaru 40 lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami ya faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne wanda ke tsaye a kan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Majalisar, yankin gudanarwa da ke ƙasa da lardin, tana da kimanin yawan jama'a 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kamun kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggula.
Hakanan hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi yana mayar da hankali a Morowali, a kan gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun yi watsi da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, a cewar Hukumar Rage Mulki ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, wani tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya hallaka daruruwan gidaje a Donggula.
Wani tsunami kuma ya buge yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan Ring na Wuta na Pacific kuma ana buga ta da girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan tsofaffi da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Babban girgizar kasa a yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya buge ƙasashe 14, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a bakin tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Jerin girgizar ƙasa da karfi sun buga gabar yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, daga bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girman 6.8 ya kai kudu da Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, wanda ya haifar da tsunami da ya fada a bakin tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Bala'i mai girma 7.6 ya faru kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
An kashe mutane fiye da 1,100.
2010: Bala'i mai girma 7.5 ya kai daya daga cikin tsibirin Mentawai, daga Sumatra, wanda ya haifar da tsunami har zuwa mita 10 wanda ya hallaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kimanin 300.
2016: Girgizar ƙasa ta buga Pidie Jaya regency a Aceh, yana haifar da hallaka da firgita yayin da mutane suka tunatar da hallakar girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekara ta 2004.
Babu tsunami da aka kaddamar a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da 100 sun kashe da gine-ginen da suka fadi.
2018: Babban girgizar ƙasa ya kai tsibirin yawon bude ido na Indonesia na Lombok, inda ya kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Bala'in ya hallaka dubban gine-gine kuma ya bar dubban yawon bude ido na ɗan lokaci.
