Saipov, mai shekaru 30, da ake zargin ya yi amfani da motar haya ta House Depot don gudanar da hari a kan hanyar bike tare da babbar hanya ta Yammacin Yamma a Lower Manhattan, yana motsawa masu tafiya da keke a hanyarsa a Oktoba.
