Wadannan laifuka biyu suna da watakila hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardun kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar shari'a ta tarayya ta kaddamar da Saipov tare da zargin 22 wanda ya hada da zargin kisan kai takwas don taimakon racketing, yawanci masu gabatar da kara a cikin laifuka da aka shirya, da kuma zargin tashin hankali da hallaka motocin motoci.
