A karo na ƙarshe da aka aiwatar da hukuncin kisa a cikin wani shari'ar tarayya ta New York shine a shekarar 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata biyu sun kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin yin makirci don yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a lokacin yakin sanyi shekaru biyu kafin.
